{"tid":723991,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"[牙痛]牙痛到想剝","createTime":"2018-06-30T16:43:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T16:12:37.000Z","uid":35281,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1c574ef809bf558e5d862a8c4e2f8ecfd1c1889d","tid":723991,"uid":35281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T16:43:02.000Z","msg":"右上第二大臼齒(最入 智慧齒隔離)呢幾日都陰啲陰啲咁痛 <br />\n到琴晚訓訓下痛到醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本身隻牙都蛀得好犀利 <br />\n而且之前睇牙醫話隔離隻智慧齒仲未生得弱智住<br />\n所以我諗應該都係第二大臼齒嘅問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係好撚痛呀師父<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為冇錢做杜牙根同植牙而且短時間內都唔會有咁多錢<br />\n所以好撚想剝咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問下剝咗呢隻牙除咗食野唔方便同隔離隻牙會移位之外會唔會仲有其他問題?<br />\n<br />\n嚟緊7月1同2都係紅日 搵唔到診所有開門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唉 早知細個努力啲刷牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd45ebfb966ea05a1f0d105c1a6b69414f5a7d28","tid":723991,"uid":179547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T16:45:31.000Z","msg":"紅日點會冇診所開"},{"pid":"09a609470136fcc22faf6fa9d9fc63b4317123a7","tid":723991,"uid":152041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T16:46:22.000Z","msg":"愛康健<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08e9d53a834b8c271a601f266637b95ba20f6b19","tid":723991,"uid":27510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T16:48:14.000Z","msg":"會唔會係隻智慧齒頂住前面隻牙所以你覺得痛"},{"pid":"f780e2ab74a6c745d803f72ecd354d4b9829b168","tid":723991,"uid":35281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd45ebfb966ea05a1f0d105c1a6b69414f5a