By":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T16:51:14.000Z","msg":"我依隻牙都蛀到入心，諗住畀幾千蚊杜牙根<br />\n始終剝一隻就冇一隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T16:55:12.000Z","msg":"之前問過上第二大臼齒呢個位杜牙根要萬幾蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打去邊杜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf53aa822529e04a76fabfb1ca9b1c2442b6d697","tid":723991,"uid":47160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T16:57:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我依隻牙都蛀到入心，諗住畀幾千蚊杜牙根<br />\n始終剝一隻就冇一隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>之前問過上第二大臼齒呢個位杜牙根要萬幾蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打去邊杜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我未問價，但我阿媽話之前隻大牙社牙根要5千蚊，我估差唔多掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"288e16e0323b5e601f1aab6f7d0c8dfdf472e144","tid":723991,"uid":27510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1188e0dd14edea8ae3449ec9b52306e2ad06f7b7","tid":723991,"uid":35281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08e9d53a834b8c271a601f266637b95ba20f6b19","tid":723991,"uid":27510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T16:48:14.000Z","msg":"會唔會係隻智慧齒頂住前面隻牙所以你覺得痛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T16:52:21.000Z","msg":"其實諗過都有可能<br />\n只係因為隻臼齒蛀得太勁而且冇錢所以想剝咗佢一了百了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T16:59:03.000Z","msg":"其實隻牙咁入你剝左都唔會話好大影響<br />\n起碼露齒笑都唔會比人見到有個洞先<br />\n不過有錢既就順便搞埋隻智慧齒佢啦，一了百了<br />\n我果陣係間中痛，唔理，之後比佢頂到牙肉勁痛野都唔想食又訓唔到覺先去剝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要正值新年等撚左勁多日先有診所開工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5b3c70ef7981b10329626e872380001b56b3da4","tid":723991,"uid":179547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e58e7b9330e1241cbd