oji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T17:03:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用牙簽輕輕桔一下都有啲痛係咪已經太遲"},{"pid":"bb87eec55e7209c7eb3c564fad7a1fed2506ee09","tid":723991,"uid":35281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3325c5a9c9372dbf40161657fb4bc0aafd9087ff","tid":723991,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T16:54:16.000Z","msg":"以前細個補隻牙而家崩左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔痛但係成日想用利頂佢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T17:04:05.000Z","msg":"上年呢隻牙有窿補過<br />\n但係早幾個月啲填充物成粒甩咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲未去補<br />\n而家成日食完野攝住啲殘渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dd8651569ca5a9ba144b09586393903928fc50e","tid":723991,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T17:05:04.000Z","msg":"最入就剝咗去算啦 一了百了 我都剝過最入大牙 進食完全冇影響"},{"pid":"82830b09b8bdeaabfdf275aeffe87606af22c685","tid":723991,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb87eec55e7209c7eb3c564fad7a1fed2506ee09","tid":723991,"uid":35281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3325c5a9c9372dbf40161657fb4bc0aafd9087ff","tid":723991,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T16:54:16.000Z","msg":"以前細個補隻牙而家崩左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔痛但係成日想用利頂佢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T17:04:05.000Z","msg":"上年呢隻牙有窿補過<br />\n但係早幾個月啲填充物成粒甩咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲未去補<br />\n而家成日食完野攝住啲殘渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"